that $N_L^{(3/2)}$ effects in cross-correlation will be detected with high\nsignificance when using data of future surveys and could affect systematic\neffects marginalization in cosmic shear measurements mimicking galaxy intrinsic\nalignment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Jun 2019 17:28:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Oct 2019 14:53:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-30"}
