-like opacity effect. Ultimately, the $n_2$ population is\nregulated by the enhancement or lack of downward Ly$\\alpha$ flux, which\ncoherently shifts the formation height of both diagnostics to regions with\ndifferent temperature, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Jun 2019 23:40:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-27"}
