bjects. Only talking about the percent in \\frac{|\\Delta\nz|}{1+z_{i}}<0.3, there is still large room for further improvement in the\nphotometric redshift estimation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Jun 2019 01:23:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 21 Nov 2019 08:51:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-05"}
