es as the first step towards quantitatively\nunderstanding construction projects' impact on a quality of life (QoL)\nindicator (specifically emergency response times) in urban settings.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Jun 2019 01:29:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-24"}
