tory size by 2.2-16 times compared to\nstate-of-the-art systems (e.g. IBM's Mirage and Hemera) with significant VMI\npublish and slight retrieval performance improvement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Jun 2019 13:08:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Jul 2019 17:19:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-30"}
